To Schismatiques is applyed that Text in the

 54th. Psalm: Veniet mors super eos & descendunt vivi in infernum: Death shall come upon them;
                        Meaning the people, upon whom fire came down from Heaven, and consumed them, saith St Augustiine; and they shall descend quick into Hell. Quid est viventes scientes quia pereunt & tamen pereuntes: The Priests who know they perish if they live not within the Church, and yet will perish; these Priests, Descendunt viventes, quia ipsi Scripturas tractant, &c. Descend into Hell, saith St. Augustine, because they handled the Scriptures, and by reading them every day, knew well the Catholique Church was that which was so diffused over the whole Earth, that nothing can be said against it.
